			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">With the Diamond Prism of Companionship augment from LDoN (Takish 760 points) the Epic Pet goes from Light Blue con at level 65 to Dark Blue. Although I use my air pet a lot, I seem to end up going back to the Epic Pet when the going gets tough. Its combo of tanking ability, procs and innate DS give it an edge on a lot of the 60+ pets. 
<br />

<br />
With the Augment focus mentioned above, I have noticed the following:
<br />
ALL pets regenerate 5% per tick.
<br />
Air Pet max hit is 85
<br />
Epic Pet max hit is 83
<br />
Fire Pet max hit is 83
<br />
Water Pet max hit is 83 (max backstab is 249)
<br />
Earth Pet max hit is 81<br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=45542" target="_blank" class="postlink"><img src="http://deprugh.home.mindspring.com/Brim-Sig.gif" border="0" />
<br />
Brimz' Stuff</a>
<br />
